36#define DNS_PORTLIST_MAGIC ISC_MAGIC('P','L','S','T')
37#define DNS_VALID_PORTLIST(p) ISC_MAGIC_VALID(p, DNS_PORTLIST_MAGIC)
38
39typedef struct dns_element {
40 in_port_t port;
41 uint16_t flags;
42} dns_element_t;
43
44struct dns_portlist {
45 unsigned int magic;
46 isc_mem_t *mctx;
47 isc_refcount_t refcount;
48 isc_mutex_t lock;
49 dns_element_t *list;
50 unsigned int allocated;
51 unsigned int active;
52};
53
54#define DNS_PL_INET 0x0001
55#define DNS_PL_INET6 0x0002
56#define DNS_PL_ALLOCATE 16
57
58static int
59compare(const void *arg1, const void *arg2) {
60 const dns_element_t *e1 = (const dns_element_t *)arg1;
61 const dns_element_t *e2 = (const dns_element_t *)arg2;
62
63 if (e1->port < e2->port)
64 return (-1);
65 if (e1->port > e2->port)
66 return (1);
67 return (0);
68}
69
70isc_result_t
71dns_portlist_create(isc_mem_t *mctx, dns_portlist_t **portlistp) {
72 dns_portlist_t *portlist;
73
74 REQUIRE(portlistp != NULL && *portlistp == NULL);
75
76 portlist = isc_mem_get(mctx, sizeof(*portlist));
77 if (portlist == NULL)
78 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
79 isc_mutex_init(&portlist->lock);
80 isc_refcount_init(&portlist->refcount, 1);
81 portlist->list = NULL;
82 portlist->allocated = 0;
83 portlist->active = 0;
84 portlist->mctx = NULL;
85 isc_mem_attach(mctx, &portlist->mctx);
86 portlist->magic = DNS_PORTLIST_MAGIC;
87 *portlistp = portlist;
88 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
89}
90
91static dns_element_t *
92find_port(dns_element_t *list, unsigned int len, in_port_t port) {
93 unsigned int xtry = len / 2;
94 unsigned int min = 0;
95 unsigned int max = len - 1;
96 unsigned int last = len;
97
98 for (;;) {
99 if (list[xtry].port == port)
100 return (&list[xtry]);
101 if (port > list[xtry].port) {
102 if (xtry == max)
103 break;
104 min = xtry;
105 xtry = xtry + (max - xtry + 1) / 2;
106 INSIST(xtry <= max);
107 if (xtry == last)
108 break;
109 last = min;
110 } else {
111 if (xtry == min)
112 break;
113 max = xtry;
114 xtry = xtry - (xtry - min + 1) / 2;
115 INSIST(xtry >= min);
116 if (xtry == last)
117 break;
118 last = max;
119 }
120 }
121 return (NULL);
122}
123
124isc_result_t
125dns_portlist_add(dns_portlist_t *portlist, int af, in_port_t port) {
126 dns_element_t *el;
127 isc_result_t result;
128
129 REQUIRE(DNS_VALID_PORTLIST(portlist));
130 REQUIRE(af == AF_INET || af == AF_INET6);
131
132 LOCK(&portlist->lock);
133 if (portlist->active != 0) {
134 el = find_port(portlist->list, portlist->active, port);
135 if (el != NULL) {
136 if (af == AF_INET)
137 el->flags |= DNS_PL_INET;
138 else
139 el->flags |= DNS_PL_INET6;
140 result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
141 goto unlock;
142 }
143 }
144
145 if (portlist->allocated <= portlist->active) {
146 unsigned int allocated;
147 allocated = portlist->allocated + DNS_PL_ALLOCATE;
148 el = isc_mem_get(portlist->mctx, sizeof(*el) * allocated);
149 if (el == NULL) {
150 result = ISC_R_NOMEMORY;
151 goto unlock;
152 }
153 if (portlist->list != NULL) {
154 memmove(el, portlist->list,
155 portlist->allocated * sizeof(*el));
156 isc_mem_put(portlist->mctx, portlist->list,
157 portlist->allocated * sizeof(*el));
158 }
159 portlist->list = el;
160 portlist->allocated = allocated;
161 }
162 portlist->list[portlist->active].port = port;
163 if (af == AF_INET)
164 portlist->list[portlist->active].flags = DNS_PL_INET;
165 else
166 portlist->list[portlist->active].flags = DNS_PL_INET6;
167 portlist->active++;
168 qsort(portlist->list, portlist->active, sizeof(*el), compare);
169 result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
170 unlock:
171 UNLOCK(&portlist->lock);
172 return (result);
173}
174
175void
176dns_portlist_remove(dns_portlist_t *portlist, int af, in_port_t port) {
177 dns_element_t *el;
178
179 REQUIRE(DNS_VALID_PORTLIST(portlist));
180 REQUIRE(af == AF_INET || af == AF_INET6);
181
182 LOCK(&portlist->lock);
183 if (portlist->active != 0) {
184 el = find_port(portlist->list, portlist->active, port);
185 if (el != NULL) {
186 if (af == AF_INET)
187 el->flags &= ~DNS_PL_INET;
188 else
189 el->flags &= ~DNS_PL_INET6;
190 if (el->flags == 0) {
191 *el = portlist->list[portlist->active];
192 portlist->active--;
193 qsort(portlist->list, portlist->active,
194 sizeof(*el), compare);
195 }
196 }
197 }
198 UNLOCK(&portlist->lock);
199}
200
201bool
202dns_portlist_match(dns_portlist_t *portlist, int af, in_port_t port) {
203 dns_element_t *el;
204 bool result = false;
205
206 REQUIRE(DNS_VALID_PORTLIST(portlist));
207 REQUIRE(af == AF_INET || af == AF_INET6);
208 LOCK(&portlist->lock);
209 if (portlist->active != 0) {
210 el = find_port(portlist->list, portlist->active, port);
211 if (el != NULL) {
212 if (af == AF_INET && (el->flags & DNS_PL_INET) != 0)
213 result = true;
214 if (af == AF_INET6 && (el->flags & DNS_PL_INET6) != 0)
215 result = true;
216 }
217 }
218 UNLOCK(&portlist->lock);
219 return (result);
220}
221
222void
223dns_portlist_attach(dns_portlist_t *portlist, dns_portlist_t **portlistp) {
224
225 REQUIRE(DNS_VALID_PORTLIST(portlist));
226 REQUIRE(portlistp != NULL && *portlistp == NULL);
227
228 isc_refcount_increment(&portlist->refcount);
229 *portlistp = portlist;
230}
231
232void
233dns_portlist_detach(dns_portlist_t **portlistp) {
234 REQUIRE(portlistp != NULL && DNS_VALID_PORTLIST(*portlistp));
235 dns_portlist_t *portlist = *portlistp;
236 *portlistp = NULL;
237
238 if (isc_refcount_decrement(&portlist->refcount) == 1) {
239 portlist->magic = 0;
240 isc_refcount_destroy(&portlist->refcount);
241 if (portlist->list != NULL)
242 isc_mem_put(portlist->mctx, portlist->list,
243 portlist->allocated *
244 sizeof(*portlist->list));
245 isc_mutex_destroy(&portlist->lock);
246 isc_mem_putanddetach(&portlist->mctx, portlist,
247 sizeof(*portlist));
248 }
